Package org.wiyn.etc.inputSpectrum.gui

Class Summary
BlackbodyPanel This class provides a panel for including (or excluding) a blackbody spectrum in the target spectrum calculation and for setting its temperature.
EmissionLinePanel This class provides a panel for including (or excluding) an emission line in the target spectrum calculation and for setting its properties.
FlatFnPanel  
FluxNormalizationPanel  
InputSpectrumSelection  
KC96Panel  
KuruczModelPanel This class provides a panel for including (or excluding) a Kurucz model spectrum in the target spectrum calculation and for setting all its properties.
LunarPropertiesPanel This class provides the panel for setting the lunar properties.
PowerLawPanel This class provides a panel for including (or excluding) a power law spectrum in the target spectrum calculation and for setting its index.
SolarPropertiesPanel This class provides the panel for setting the solar properties.
SpectrumGenerationPane This class provides the panel for generating a target and a sky spectrum.
SpectrumPanel The panel for entering the relevant data for some spectrum can be divided in three parts.
UBVRIMagnitudesPanel This class provides the panel for the target and sky spectrum magnitudes in the U, B, V, R and I band.
UserSuppliedSpectrumPanel This class provides a panel for including (or excluding) a user-supplied spectrum in the target spectrum calculation and for setting its URL.
